        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>ATF Accountability Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes a federal statutory process for licensed gun dealers, importers, and manufacturers to appeal rulings and determinations by the Bureau of Alcohol, Tobacco, Firearms and Explosives. <br> </p>]]>
        </text>
